    "body": "_This issue is good for beginners. Read [Making your first pull request](https://github.com/ember-learn/guides-source/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#making-your-first-pull-request) and ask for help if you run into issues! Experienced contributors are asked to search for other things to fix._\r\n\r\nIn [this guide](https://github.com/ember-learn/guides-source/blob/master/guides/release/templates/input-helpers.md) we show using a keyPress event with a checkbox. That seems odd since a click will not trigger updates.\r\n\r\nReplace this example with a text input, try it in an app to see if it works, and open a PR with the change. Make sure to check the written sections around the example to see if any of the explanations need to be changed too.\r\n\r\nHere's the example that needs to be refactored:\r\n\r\n```\r\n<Input @type=\"checkbox\" @keyPress={{action \"updateName\"}} />\r\n```\r\n\r\nSomething like this will work:\r\n\r\n```\r\n<Input @type=\"text\" @keyPress={{action \"updateName\"}} />\r\n```",
