    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "active_lock_reason": null,
    "body": "This repository would benefit from having some Percy screenshots!\r\n\r\nFor an example of the work that should be done, see https://github.com/ember-learn/guides-source/blob/master/.github/workflows/ci.yml and search for \"percy\"\r\n\r\nTo do:\r\n- install the percy addon\r\n- Edit the GitHub Action to have the key and run the test\r\n- Add percy snapshots to the tests for the index page and one of the subpages such as https://help-wanted.emberjs.com/emberjs\r\n\r\nNote that you may not see the Percy tests running in your PR, since that repo may or may not be enabled already in the Percy & GitHub management dashboards. The core team will add it after you open your PR, and we'll re-run the tests to see if it shows up!\r\n\r\n",
    "performed_via_github_app": null,
